<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Deposit - CHAINX</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
  <style>
    body {
      background: white;
      font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 40px 20px;
      color: #333;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 60px auto;
      background: white;
      padding: 40px;
      border-radius: 15px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      text-align: center;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      color: #2c3f51;
    }
    .header .logo {
      width: 60px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .brand {
      font-size: 2rem;
      color: #2c3f51;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    h2 {
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      color: #2c3f51;
    }
    .disabled-message {
      color: red;
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      margin-top: 40px;
      background: #f8d7da;
      border-left: 5px solid #d9534f;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 25px 20px;
      display: inline-block;
    }
    .info {
      background: #f3f3f3;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      border-left: 5px solid #2c3f51;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
      color: #555;
      font-size: 16px;
      display: inline-block;
      text-align: left;
    }
    .back-btn {
      display: block;
      width: fit-content;
      margin: 30px auto 0;
      padding: 12px 25px;
      background-color: #1f3a54;
      color: white;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 25px;
      font-size: 16px;
      text-align: center;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background 0.3s ease;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .back-btn:hover {
      background-color: #1c2e40;
    }
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      body {
        padding: 20px 10px;
      }
      .container {
        padding: 30px 20px;
      }
      .header h1 {
        font-size: 2rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="info">
      <strong>Notice:</strong> For your security, please contact customer support to confirm your account information before making any deposit.<br>
      After a successful transfer, provide the transfer slip to customer service to update your platform account.<br>
      The payee's name and transfer amount must match the provided account information.<br>
      If you have any issues, please contact our online customer service.
    </div>
   
